TRAVEL-OPENBUS _ PARIS _ In Paris, it is called L'OpenTour; in
Vienna, it's the Hop-On Hop-Off; in London, it's The Big Bus. What
they all are are inexpensive, accommodating ways to tour cities on
your own time, at your own pace. Here's how they work. (Kleinberg,
Cox News Service) MOVED. WITH PHOTO.
