travel guide has your ticket to a post-academic rite of passage:
Exploring Europe by train. The Great Outdoor Recreation Pages
(GORP.com) has launched ``Eurailing: A Great American Tradition,''
A nuts-and-bolts primer on the Europe's rail pass system. We
explore the site and briefly look at what other Web Travel guides
are doing to attract young wanderers.(Hamilton, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
