<P>
   ETHIOPIA-ERITREA (Nairobi, Kenya) _ Eritrea announced Thursday
that it will pull out of all contested territory, bringing the war
with Ethiopia close to an end. By Ian Fisher. (With map)
</P>
<P>
   PERU-POLITICS (Lima) _ President Alberto K. Fujimori has
strongly hinted that Peru will postpone Sunday's presidential
runoff election in order to satisfy critics of the election
process. By Clifford Krauss.
</P>
