stunned that undercover agents using fake cards identifying them as
law officers were able to penetrate 19 federal buildings, promises
to revamp her department's security system. That means guards will
stop giving preferential treatment to fellow law officers. We check
other federal agencies where security was breached. By MARK HELM.
