<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    HOUSE COMMITTEE APPROVES PHASE-OUT OF FEDERAL ESTATE TAXES
 &HT;    By LARRY LIPMAN
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
