<P>
   &UR; (FIRST OPTIONAL TRIM _ 175 WORDS _ BEGINS HERE AT 300) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   The sheikh's armed protectors searched the horizon for Israeli
troops. There were none to be seen. Just that morning mist and the
