</P>
<P>
   A gross-out comedy with Norm Macdonald as an underappreciated
chauffeur who plots revenge against his boss by kidnapping her dog.
The word ``crass'' does not begin to describe this laughless black
comedy. This film sat on the shelf for more than a year. The
question is : why release it at all? (John Hartl, Seattle Times)1
hour, 30 minutes. F
