on the city's daily newspaper publishers, asking a federal judge to
permanently bar not only the Hearst Corp.'s purchase of the San
Francisco Chronicle but also its sale of the Examiner. By SETH
ROSENFELD. (Already filed.)
</P>
<P>
   SPORTS (``s'' category)
</P>
<P>
